---
/**
 * Case Studies index. Per BRIEF v4 Section 9.
 */
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout page="caseStudies" path="/case-studies">
  <div class="coord-strip" slot="coord-strip">
    <span>Case studies <span class="dot-pink">●</span> Documented outcomes</span>
    <span>Cross-industry · Operator work</span>
  </div>

  <div class="page-label green">
    <span>/case-studies</span>
  </div>

  <h1 class="page-title">Case studies.</h1>

  <p class="bio-lead">
    Documented outcomes and methodologies from cross-industry operator work. Each case study covers problem, constraints, strategy, system built, results, and what transferred to subsequent work. Some client work is confidential; published case studies document what can be disclosed.
  </p>

  <section class="case-study-list">
    <article class="case-study-preview">
      <h2 class="h2-rosa"><a href="/case-studies/vida">VIDA Wellness & Beauty Center</a></h2>
      <p class="case-study-meta">Medical Tourism · 2023 to 2026 · Chief Sales and Marketing Officer</p>
      <p>How Cost Per Surgery was reduced from $1,300 to $490 (a 62% reduction) at a Tijuana medical tourism provider serving primarily US patients, while cutting overall ad spend by 20%. The methodology that became Tersefy.</p>
      <a href="/case-studies/vida" class="read-link">Read the case study →</a>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="case-study-coming">
    <h3>More case studies in development</h3>
    <p>Additional case studies documenting Visit Boca tourism brand launch (City of Boca del Río), UNETE cross-border fundraising, and Agency Gallo Reyna brand campaigns are in preparation.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
